Director of Liberty Global plc -ss A Or (NASDAQ:LBTYA), Malone John C, buys 384,673 shares worth $8,385,680
According to Liberty Global plc -ss A Or's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Jul 07 06:16 PM, company Director, Malone John C disclosed buying 384,673 shares at a cost of $21.80. At the time of this transaction (Jul 07), this trade was worth $8,385,680 in total. As of Jul 07, Malone John C now owns 2,537,101 shares in total worth about $79,259,035.24. 
For the last few recent trades made by Liberty Global plc -ss A Or (NASDAQ:LBTYA) Director, Malone John C, we have the following information:




SEC Form 4 filing: Jul 05: Bought 139,052 shares at the rate of $21.74 per share. Total worth of this trade was $3,022,813. Total number of shares owned as of Jul 05 were 2,086,609
SEC Form 4 filing: Jul 06: Bought 223,186 shares at the rate of $21.76 per share. Total worth of this trade was $4,856,225. Total number of shares owned as of Jul 06 were 2,232,363




